                            (default: auto — skips install if spectacular is already
                             available upstream/globally/as a plugin, else project)
      --no-skill            Alias for --skill-scope none
      --update              Re-download latest skill release and update skills.lock
  -h, --help                Show this help

Always-set (scaffolded regardless of kit/flags):
